	<td class="zheadline" colspan="2">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="znewsdate">9.10.2021 - </span><b>Retro Oldera</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td class="znewsbody" colspan="2"><p>Welcome<strong>&nbsp;to all Olderians who have come to enjoy the best of what classic Tibia has to offer!</strong></p>
<p>The Oldera&nbsp;&nbsp;runes only created by the players themselves, accurate 7.4 formulas and tons more this is guaranteed to bring back all the good memories of the past!</p>
<div><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Oldera will launched with Open-PVP&nbsp;server:</strong></span></div>
<ul>
<li><img src="https://mastercores.com/images/flags/us.png" width="18" height="12" />&nbsp;<strong>Oldera</strong>&nbsp;-&nbsp;America Central,&nbsp;<strong>USA</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><em><strong>Meaning they will never reset!, Once your character is created, it will be with you forever!</strong></em></p>
<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://www.noxiousot.com/images/sdivider.png" alt="sdivider.png" /></p>
<div><strong>Oldera features:</strong></div>
<ul>
<li>Non-stackable runes/fluids</li>
<li>No runes from NPCs</li>
<li>Accurate 7.4 formulas</li>
<li><strong>Free premium&nbsp;system</strong></li>
<li>Traditional promotion system</li>
<li>No runes on hotkeys</li>
<li>No wands/rods</li>
<li>7.4&nbsp;map&nbsp;+ Port Hope + Custom Zones</li>
<li>Anti-lag systems to ensure smooth gameplay</li>
<li>Free Spells</li>
<li>Shared Exp in Party + Bonus Vocation (100%)</li>
<li>Tasks System</li>
<li>Cast system bonus 10% exp</li>
</ul>
<p>For further information about Oldera features, have a look at the&nbsp;<a href="../?server" target="_blank" rel="noopener">information</a>&nbsp;page!</p>
<p><strong>Rates:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>2x Experience</li>
<li>2x Loot</li>
<li>1x Magic</li>
<li>2x Skills</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Will Oldera shut down / reboot at some point?</strong></p>
<p>No, the server will be long-term, having been online for over a year without a single reboot, I can safely assure you that Oldera will NEVER shut down or reboot!</p>
<p><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0042a0; font-weight: bold; background-color: #fcecd3; font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="https://discordapp.com/invite/GW4Cc9b" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; width: 28px; height: 28px;" src="https://i.imgur.com/Se2pveP.png" /></a><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial; background-color: #fcecd3; font-size: 16px;">If you're new to the community, join the&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0042a0; font-weight: bold; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="https://discord.com/invite/BNTVV3NTA9" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Oldera Discord</a>&nbsp;server to chat with other players and staff!</span></p>
<p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; color: #006600; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; background-color: #fcecd3;">Oldera will launch on November 05, 18:00&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: #fcecd3; color: #006600; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;"><img style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; background-color: #ffffff;" src="https://mastercores.com/images/flags/us.png" width="18" height="12" />.</span></p>
<p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial; background-color: #fcecd3;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #cc0000;">Character-creations are open now!</span></span></p>
<p>Sincerely,<br />Oldera Staff</p>
